<title>wjhk rby ạ̉mạmy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wjhk rby ạ̉mạmy nwrk ḍạʾ ẓlạmy(2)
 qsmty ạ̉nt mrạmy mnqdẖy ạ̉bgẖy rḍạk(2)
 mnqdẖy ạ̉bgẖy rḍạk
 1-mnk yạ nbʿ ạlsrwr fạḍ fy qlby ḥbwry(2)
 yạ mlyky lldhwr swf ạ̉tbʿ kẖṭạk
 2-ṣkẖrty ạ̉nt ḥbyby ḥṣny fy ḍyqy mjyby(2)
 rby qd ṣrt nṣyby lys fy ạlʿmr swạk
 3-ạ̉dkẖlny ạlʿmq rby ạ̹gẖsln qlby wlby(2)
 ạ̉smw fyk yʿlw ḥby ạ̉nsẖd lḥn smạk</lyrics>
</song>